        p.name productName,

2020-09-05 17:36:47.896 DEBUG 15444 --- [io-8080-exec-10]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,
        p.is_deleted ,
        p.description 
    from
        product p 
    left join
        category c 
            on p.category_id = c.id 
    where
        p.is_deleted = false     
        and(
            upper(p.name) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')     
            or upper(c.name ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')
        )     
    order by
        p.last_updated_stamp DESC limit ?

        name supplierName,
        phone_number phoneNumbe,
        email,
        address  
    from
        supplier s 
    where
        is_deleted = false   
        and (
            upper(code) like upper(concat('%', ?, '%'))   
            or upper(name) like upper(concat('%', ?, '%'))   
            or upper(email) like upper(concat('%', ?, '%'))   
            or upper(phone_number) like upper(concat('%', ?, '%'))   
            or upper(address) like upper(concat('%', ?, '%'))
        ) 
    order by
        s.last_updated_stamp desc limit ?
2020-09-05 17:36:48.272 DEBUG 15444 --- [nio-8080-exec-6]  org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    select
        CAST(p.id as varchar) productId,
        code productCode,
        p.name productName,
        c.name categoryName,
        price,
        image_link linkImg,
        inventory_number warehouseQuantity,
        p.is_deleted ,
        p.description 
    from
        product p 
    left join
        category c 
            on p.category_id = c.id 
    where
        p.is_deleted = false     
        and(
            upper(p.name) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')     
            or upper(c.name ) like concat('%',upper(?),'%')
        )     
    order by
        p.last_updated_stamp DESC limit ?
